      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every aspect of this motorcar\u2014from its flawless exterior finish to its pristine, smoke-free interior\u2014has been maintained to the most exacting standards. Mechanically superior and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, it offers a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection. This is not merely a pre-owned vehicle; it is a definitive statement of luxury and meticulous care.",
